Class UpdateStatisticsDTO

java.lang.Object
com.example.full_connection.DTO.UpdateStatisticsDTO
public class UpdateStatisticsDTO extends Object
Data Transfer Object for Updating Statistics. Contains various metrics related to student performance and sessions.
